WEBVTT

00:00:00.716 --> 00:00:02.916
[Countdown is a non-profit
global collaboration

00:00:02.916 --> 00:00:05.756
to champion and accelerate solutions
to the climate crisis,

00:00:05.796 --> 00:00:07.036
turning ideas into action.

00:00:07.036 --> 00:00:09.596
It is an initiative intended
to educate and activate.]

00:00:09.636 --> 00:00:11.556
[Everyone has a vital role to play.]

00:00:15.916 --> 00:00:18.556
Don Cheadle: There's a story
we've been writing together

00:00:18.556 --> 00:00:19.756
for hundreds of years.

00:00:19.796 --> 00:00:22.236
Voiceover: Oil companies
compete with each other ...

00:00:22.276 --> 00:00:23.476
DC: It's about all of us.

00:00:24.556 --> 00:00:26.716
It takes place right here.

00:00:28.636 --> 00:00:31.316
It started for many of us
as economies were built.